featureType.name: SeamapAus_WA_predictedHab_SWCorner_obs
featureType.title: Benthic annotations from video observations in SW Corner (WA) - extract from GlobalArchive
featureType.abstract: This dataset is an extract from GlobalArchive (https://globalarchive.org/) of publicly available benthic habitat annotations from stereo-BRUV drops in the SW Corner area of Western Australia. These validation points were used as inputs to predicted benthic habitat mapping for this region. This layer has been created for use in a layer package in combination with habitat models. GlobalArchive should be used for download access, and to view more data for the region.
